          About This Platform

          Philosophy

          This is a 100% private, offline-first application. All your data is stored directly in this HTML file and in your browser's local storage. Nothing is ever sent to any server.

          Features

          • Public & Private Posts: You control what the world sees. Mark posts as public or keep them private, accessible only via a secure token.
          • Full Admin Control: The dashboard provides a central place to manage all content and settings.
          • No Database, No Server: The entire website is contained within this single HTML file. To back it up, simply save the file.

          Disclaimer

          This tool is provided as-is. The developer assumes no liability for any data loss. You are solely responsible for your own data and actions.

          Wiki Syntax Guide

          Use the following syntax in the editor to create special links.

          [[Topic Name]]

          Creates a link to another post. If the post exists, the link will be active. If not, it will be shown as a broken link.

          [[Category:Category Name]]

          Adds a category label to the post and creates a link that filters all posts by that category.
